      "updated": 1776025358732,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Big Table\n- it stores thumbnails for all videos\n- Each thumbnail size ~ 5kb\n- big table is best choice as it \n  saves alot of disk seeks (I/O)\n  because it stores files in a block (SSTables)\n  at one sequential place in disk which help avoid \n  multiple reads at different places.\n- it has high throughput for small reads which is\n  best for our case\n   ",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Big Table\n- it stores thumbnails for all videos\n- Each thumbnail size ~ 5kb\n- big table is best choice as it \n  saves alot of disk seeks (I/O)\n  because it stores files in a block (SSTables)\n  at one sequential place in disk which help avoid \n  multiple reads at different places.\n- it has high throughput for small reads which is\n  best for our case\n   ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
