      "updated": 1776600904077,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Cache\n- we can most frequently watch video,\n  & video metadata\n- we can use caching strategy\n  to save load on server for \n  frequently accessed contents.\n- LRU cache eviction policy will \n  be good choice here to remove\n  Unnecessary data. & Cache only stuff\n  that's useful.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Cache\n- we can most frequently watch video,\n  & video metadata\n- we can use caching strategy\n  to save load on server for \n  frequently accessed contents.\n- LRU cache eviction policy will \n  be good choice here to remove\n  Unnecessary data. & Cache only stuff\n  that's useful.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
